Package com.hp.autonomy.frontend.reports.powerpoint.dto

Provides data transfer objects (DTOs) to represent data from various types of visualizations.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ComposableElement
    Marker interface to indicate a visualization which can be rendered into a ReportData report.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Anchor
    Anchor points to use when drawing a report.
    DategraphData
    DTO to represent time-series data to plot on a xy scatterplot chart with time on the x-axis.
    DategraphData.Row
    A DTO representing a data series in a date chart.
    ListData
    DTO to represent a list of documents.
    ListData.Document
    DTO for a single document.
    MapData
    DTO to represent a map.
    MapData.Marker  
    MapData.Polygon  
    ReportData
    A DTO representing a composite report consisting of one or more children.
    ReportData.Child
    A DTO representing an individual visualization to render in a report, with bounds and an optional title.
    SunburstData
    DTO to represent a one-level Sunburst chart
    TableData
    DTO to represent a table of data.
    TextData
    DTO to represent text data to use in reports.
    TextData.Paragraph
    DTO representing a single block of text with specific formatting.
    TopicMapData
    DTO to represent topic map data.
    TopicMapData.Path
    A DTO representing an individual polygon on the topic map.
